    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just hard to believe the light will come back when everything feels so empty. people always say \"it takes time\" but time just feels like more empty space. i'm just so tired of fighting to feel okay when there's no reason to. i just want the noise in my head to stop. i just want to be at peace and not have to carry this ache every single second. it feels like the only way to actually get peace is to just... stop.",
